abstract: New York Rangers defeat Washington Capitals, 3-1, to move atop NHL Eastern Conference standings.
lead_paragraph: Cam Talbot made 28 saves, including a spectacular glove grab off a close-in shot from Nicklas Backstrom during a 5-on-3 chance, and the Rangers won at Washington, 3-1.

headline.main: Rangers Prevail to Move Into First
headline.print_headline: Rangers Win to Move Into First
